{"tid":326473,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係唔中意食太複雜既甜品？","createTime":"2017-07-18T04:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T06:41:00.000Z","uid":20209,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0e77862dcd7b2b4d7c5bbdaf802593a2fba1f9a","tid":326473,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:37:59.000Z","msg":"一個杯<br />\n兩球雪糕<br />\n淋幾隻汁，又塞堆曲奇呀水果入去<br />\n五顏六色，睇見唔開胃<br />\n自己反而中意簡單個啲芝麻糊蕃薯糖水<br />\n次次同人食都比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時寧願食山楂餅算<br />\n<br />\n有冇同好？"},{"pid":"88560487ba53da043cc4b61d3967f2bac87a8757","tid":326473,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/124329_83614bc856960e14278fdd1bd3dfe4df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F124329_83614bc856960e14278fdd1bd3dfe4df.jpg&h=8416d7b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依啲真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d231904a4c742bbd26068a08a7ee1475f0c6e93c","tid":326473,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:44:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/124329_83614bc856960e14278fdd1bd3dfe4df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F124329_83614bc856960e14278fdd1bd3dfe4df.jpg&h=8416d7b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依啲真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戇鳩港女先鐘意"},{"pid":"04bc15f266881d98e32cfb0a6d4471f208c642cb","tid":326473,"uid":92202,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/iqs8tdgy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fiqs8tdgy&h=ef950e0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26c8902b5fe9c8e01bfea308f0856443df06b716","tid":326473,"uid":44814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:54:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/124329_83614bc856960e14278fdd1bd3dfe4df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F124329_83614bc856960e14278fdd1bd3dfe4df.jpg&h=8416d7b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依啲真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戇鳩港女先鐘意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/125032_b49ef24657e260fbc25d9fc1b15766ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F125032_b49ef24657e260fbc25d9fc1b15766ab.jpg&h=cdeb1051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西式有西式嘅特別<br />\n個pastry做得好真係無得頂 配料都唔洗好複雜<br />\n以上係東京嘅Toshi Yoroizuka<br />\n<br />\n係好似松記個啲垃圾糖水舖先鳩加曲奇雪糕呀椰汁涼粉一堆乜乜77"},{"pid":"2f3c7bf4f66203d105c0e6588d53777f51f794cb","tid":326473,"uid":3649,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:01:58.000Z","msg":"我唔止甜品...我平時食嘢都唔鐘意太複雜嘅嘢...<br />\n<br />\n肉餅，蒸水蛋，蕃茄炒蛋，<br />\n意粉，簡簡單單一個漢堡扒定食我就好開心<br />\n唔知點解釋，可以話我口味比較樸素(?)<br />\n<br />\n甜品都係，五顏六色真係唔開胃，<br />\n食果陣又麻鬼煩，<br />\n我最鐘意嘅複雜糖水係雜果涼粉西米露  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（西灣河明記嘅糖水真係無得頂）<br />\n<br />\n係舊Pancake上面又加雪糕又加Cream，<br />\n都係想呃多你幾十蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d674cbf2ef59f2a996fb23242a2bb68c298d3983","tid":326473,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/124329_83614bc856960e14278fdd1bd3dfe4df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F124329_83614bc856960e14278fdd1bd3dfe4df.jpg&h=8416d7b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依啲真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戇鳩港女先鐘意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/125032_b49ef24657e260fbc25d9fc1b15766ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F125032_b49ef24657e260fbc25d9fc1b15766ab.jpg&h=cdeb1051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西式有西式嘅特別<br />\n個pastry做得好真係無得頂 配料都唔洗好複雜<br />\n以上係東京嘅Toshi Yoroizuka<br />\n<br />\n係好似松記個啲垃圾糖水舖先鳩加曲奇雪糕呀椰汁涼粉一堆乜乜77</blockquote><br />\n依個我都唔得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec282820bd7a29f53956fcc0f102188f98048401","tid":326473,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:59:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔止甜品...我平時食嘢都唔鐘意太複雜嘅嘢...<br />\n<br />\n肉餅，蒸水蛋，蕃茄炒蛋，<br />\n意粉，簡簡單單一個漢堡扒定食我就好開心<br />\n唔知點解釋，可以話我口味比較樸素(?)<br />\n<br />\n甜品都係，五顏六色真係唔開胃，<br />\n食果陣又麻鬼煩，<br />\n我最鐘意嘅複雜糖水係雜果涼粉西米露  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（西灣河明記嘅糖水真係無得頂）<br />\n<br />\n係舊Pancake上面又加雪糕又加Cream，<br />\n都係想呃多你幾十蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吹多幾句水，球雪糕都化晒水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 溶埋啲汁度見到想嘔"},{"pid":"9ce21a7f3bcfe54ccea099e172cebe0e692bd3e0","tid":326473,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/124329_83614bc856960e14278fdd1bd3dfe4df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F124329_83614bc856960e14278fdd1bd3dfe4df.jpg&h=8416d7b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依啲真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戇鳩港女先鐘意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/125032_b49ef24657e260fbc25d9fc1b15766ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F125032_b49ef24657e260fbc25d9fc1b15766ab.jpg&h=cdeb1051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西式有西式嘅特別<br />\n個pastry做得好真係無得頂 配料都唔洗好複雜<br />\n以上係東京嘅Toshi Yoroizuka<br />\n<br />\n係好似松記個啲垃圾糖水舖先鳩加曲奇雪糕呀椰汁涼粉一堆乜乜77</blockquote><br />\n依個我都唔得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但都可以試下，因為賣相幾好"},{"pid":"2d1ff5b957f736304da66139eaf5b43db458f67a","tid":326473,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:18:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔止甜品...我平時食嘢都唔鐘意太複雜嘅嘢...<br />\n<br />\n肉餅，蒸水蛋，蕃茄炒蛋，<br />\n意粉，簡簡單單一個漢堡扒定食我就好開心<br />\n唔知點解釋，可以話我口味比較樸素(?)<br />\n<br />\n甜品都係，五顏六色真係唔開胃，<br />\n食果陣又麻鬼煩，<br />\n我最鐘意嘅複雜糖水係雜果涼粉西米露  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（西灣河明記嘅糖水真係無得頂）<br />\n<br />\n係舊Pancake上面又加雪糕又加Cream，<br />\n都係想呃多你幾十蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明記好正 好鬼足料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53b42bd6741a219f5af93e9e351c7a6616260b1","tid":326473,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/124329_83614bc856960e14278fdd1bd3dfe4df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F124329_83614bc856960e14278fdd1bd3dfe4df.jpg&h=8416d7b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n依啲真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戇鳩港女先鐘意</blockquote><br />\n呢啲堆砌型甜品近年大行其道<br />\n都係因為on9港女食乜都要影要呃like所造成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n高級西餐嗰啲又唔係成日食得起<br />\n結果坊間甜品舖就間間都整呢啲出嚟"},{"pid":"2a384e0a1534e699e2ccd08ab33d61cf68020873","tid":326473,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:25:11.000Z","msg":"有冇人覺得<br />\n男人係唔應該鍾意食甜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd8071101bc4e11833e72384cdaa26bf1af0af5","tid":326473,"uid":3649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:32:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我唔止甜品...我平時食嘢都唔鐘意太複雜嘅嘢...<br />\n<br />\n肉餅，蒸水蛋，蕃茄炒蛋，<br />\n意粉，簡簡單單一個漢堡扒定食我就好開心<br />\n唔知點解釋，可以話我口味比較樸素(?)<br />\n<br />\n甜品都係，五顏六色真係唔開胃，<br />\n食果陣又麻鬼煩，<br />\n我最鐘意嘅複雜糖水係雜果涼粉西米露  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（西灣河明記嘅糖水真係無得頂）<br />\n<br />\n係舊Pancake上面又加雪糕又加Cream，<br />\n都係想呃多你幾十蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明記好正 好鬼足料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時夜晚無煮飯，行去隔離買個正正車仔麵，<br />\n再去明記買兜糖水行返筲箕灣屋企，<br />\n真係一大樂事！(肥死)<br />\n<br />\n果陣我老母聯合入院，<br />\n買過一次明記去探病，結果隔日又話要食，<br />\n人地未開門我4點走去拍佢地門問有無西米露 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29347cb508f7bed127d77fe94bac7837ac69afd","tid":326473,"uid":126339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T11:54:04.000Z","msg":"其實綠豆沙/渣渣都算複雜喎"},{"pid":"37d7dc900524a723f47d48c62480105abd37e194","tid":326473,"uid":1557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:02:53.000Z","msg":"你係要睇落簡單唔係要整法簡單，ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nme too<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36afe5db5903803a16e7219665bce9cb20181543","tid":326473,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:06:05.000Z","msg":"最鐘意楊支甘露 ,椰汁西米露 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n最憎食扮高級既 心太軟，焦糖燉蛋 ，pancake <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  送都唔食！"},{"pid":"ad61766d3300d86e0634c3aa9ae9ea3dc989dd14","tid":326473,"uid":75422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:09:36.000Z","msg":"點至叫簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一鑊熟個d 紅綠豆沙 喳咋 芝麻糊?<br />\n定煮都唔洗煮羅拔臣啫哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n理得佢複唔複雜 又唔係我煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好食就鍾意架啦"},{"pid":"dccde1b97f5b02704dbbd48295b92df7dfd52319","tid":326473,"uid":20209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T06:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點至叫簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一鑊熟個d 紅綠豆沙 喳咋 芝麻糊?<br />\n定煮都唔洗煮羅拔臣啫哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n理得佢複唔複雜 又唔係我煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好食就鍾意架啦</blockquote><br />\n冇批評 只係討論下"}]}